 Conclude |url=http://news.nationalgeographic.co.uk/news/2007/02/070202-mars-life.html |work=National Geographic News |date=2007-02-02 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221095944/http://news.nationalgeographic.co.uk/news/2007/02/070202-mars-life.html |archive-date=2014-02-21 }}</ref>。

