b |author=USGS |title=Three New Names Approved for Features on Mars |url=https://astrogeology.usgs.gov/HotTopics/index.php?/archives/447-Three-New-Names-Approved-for-Features-on-Mars.html |date=2012-05-16 |publisher=[[USGS|USGS]] |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728141903/http://astrogeology.usgs.gov/HotTopics/index.php?%2Farchives%2F447-Three-New-Names-Approved-for-Features-on-Mars.html |archive-date=2012-07-28 |access-date=2019-05-03  }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20120327">{{cite web|author=NASA Staff |title='Mount Sharp' on Mars Compared to Three Big Mountains on Earth |url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/multimedia/pia15292-Fig2.html |date=2012-03-27 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331212659/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/multimedia/pia15292-Fig2.html |archive-date=2012-03-31 }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20120328">{{cite web|last=Agle |first=D. C. |title='Mount Sharp' On Mars Links Geology's Past and Future |url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/news/msl20120328.html |date=2012-03-28 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331022443/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/news/msl20120328.html |archive-date=2012-03-31 }}</ref><ref name="Space-20120329">{{cite web|author=Staff |title=NASA's New Mars Rover Will Explore Towering 'Mount Sharp' |url=http://www.space.com/15097-mars-mountain-sharp-curiosity-rover.html |date=2012-03-29 |publisher=[[Space.com|Space.com]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120330033934/http://www.space.com/15097-mars-mountain-sharp-curiosity-rover.html |archive-date=2012-03-30 }}</ref>。

2014年12月16日，美国宇航局报告说，好奇号探测车检测到火星大气中可能为局部性的“十倍峰值”含量甲烷。“20个月内进行了十几次”样本测量的结果显示，2013年末和2014年初甲烷含量有所增加，平均“大气中甲烷含量为十亿分之七”，而在此前后，平均读数仅约为该水平的十分之一<ref name="NASA-20141216-GW"/><ref name="NYT-20141216-KC"/>。此外，在好奇号火星车分析的一块名为“坎伯兰”的岩石上所钻取的粉末中，检测到低浓度的[[氯苯|氯苯]]（CH<sub>5</sub>Cl）<ref name="NASA-20141216-GW" /><ref name="NYT-20141216-KC" />。[[火星2020|火星2020]][[毅力号火星探测器|毅力号火星车]]是[[美国宇航局|美国宇航局]]于2020年7月30日发射的[[巡视器|火星漫游者任务]]，其目的是调查火星上与[[天体生物学|天体生物学]]相关的古代环境、表面[[火星地质|地质作用]]和历史，包括评估其过去的宜居性以及在可获得地质材料中保存有[[生命印迹|生命印迹]]的可能性<ref name="Cowing_2020">{{cite web | url=http://spaceref.com/mars/science-definition-team-for-the-2020-mars-rover.html | title=Science Definition Team for the 2020 Mars Rover | first=Keith | last=Cowing | date=2012-12-21 | work=NASA | publisher=Science Ref}}</ref>。
